sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as User / Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Spark Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Controller as Spark Controller<br/>controller-runtime
    participant Driver as Spark Driver Pod<br/>7078,7079,4040/TCP
    participant Executor as Spark Executor Pods<br/>7078,7079/TCP
    participant Ingress as Ingress Controller<br/>80/443/TCP
    participant SparkConnect as SparkConnect Server<br/>15002/TCP gRPC

    Note over User,Executor: Flow 1: SparkApplication Submission

    User->>K8sAPI: POST SparkApplication CR<br/>Auth: Bearer token / kubeconfig
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-sparkoperator-k8s-io-v1beta2-sparkapplication<br/>443→9443/TCP, TLS 1.2+, K8s mTLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response (allow/deny)
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-sparkoperator-k8s-io-v1beta2-sparkapplication<br/>443→9443/TCP, TLS 1.2+, K8s mTLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated SparkApplication (defaults applied)
    K8sAPI-->>User: SparkApplication created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch SparkApplication resources<br/>443/TCP, TLS 1.2+, SA token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: SparkApplication event (Added/Modified)
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Driver Pod<br/>443/TCP, TLS 1.2+, SA token

    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate--v1-pod<br/>443→9443/TCP, TLS 1.2+, K8s mTLS
    Note right of Webhook: Applies 19 mutation functions:<br/>volumes, env vars, labels,<br/>security contexts, GPU resources,<br/>init/sidecar containers, scheduling
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated Driver Pod spec

    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Driver Pod created

    Driver->>K8sAPI: Create Executor Pods<br/>443/TCP, HTTPS, spark-operator-spark SA token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate--v1-pod (per executor)<br/>443→9443/TCP, TLS 1.2+, K8s mTLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated Executor Pod spec
    K8sAPI-->>Driver: Executor Pods created

    Driver->>Executor: Spark RPC communication<br/>7078,7079/TCP, TCP, No encryption

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create {app}-ui Service<br/>4040/TCP
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create {app}-ui Ingress<br/>80/TCP

    Note over User,Executor: Flow 2: SparkConnect Session

    User->>SparkConnect: gRPC connection<br/>15002/TCP, No encryption<br/>NetworkPolicy-restricted
    SparkConnect->>K8sAPI: Create/manage Executor Pods<br/>443/TCP, HTTPS, SA token
    SparkConnect->>Executor: Spark RPC<br/>7078,7079/TCP, TCP, No encryption

    Note over User,Ingress: Flow 3: Spark Web UI Access

    User->>Ingress: HTTP/HTTPS request<br/>80/443/TCP, Optional TLS
    Ingress->>Driver: Forward to Spark UI<br/>4040/TCP, HTTP, No auth
